A. OS name
B. Server name
C. Application/domain
D. Storage engine

Which naming improves maintainability?
A. Short random names
B. Numeric-only names
C. Logical grouping
D. Uppercase names

Which is a valid best practice?
A. One database for all apps
B. Separate databases per application
C. Multiple schemas per table
D. One table per database

Which is recommended for versioning?
A. Append version in table
B. Append version in database name
C. Rename database frequently
D. Use temporary databases

